@node History "History"
    @{fg highlight}History :@{fg text} Successive versions

@{b}Version 0.9 (november 8, 1994)@{ub}
  Preliminary version, released on the avahi site,  for the readers of the
  french mailing list (@{fg fill}amiga@sophia.inria.fr@{fg text}).
  32 modules.
  AmigaGuide documentation draft, in french.

@{b}Version 1.0 (january 8, 1995)@{ub}
  First version released on Aminet.
  54 modules.
  Complete AmigaGuide documentation, in french and in english.

@{b}Version 1.1 (may 24, 1995)@{ub}
  Second version released on Aminet.
  85 modules.
  Bug free AmigaGuide documentation, with additional index.

@endnode







